13:44.490 --> 13:46.082
I didn't do it.

13:48.620 --> 13:50.520
How did that sound?

13:56.000 --> 13:58.161
Volquartsen 3.5 compact.

13:58.200 --> 14:00.566
Weight: three pounds,
ten-shot mag,

14:00.600 --> 14:02.488
adjustable rear
and blade front--

14:02.540 --> 14:04.599
it'll take down
any man in his tracks.

14:04.640 --> 14:07.336
What if she doesn't have a FOID?

14:07.380 --> 14:09.632
Apply for one.
