14:09.680 --> 14:11.500
What if she doesn't
have 30 days?

14:11.550 --> 14:12.972
Do you have a Firearm Owner ID?

14:14.580 --> 14:16.616
Then buy it for her.

14:18.350 --> 14:21.183
