14:21.220 --> 14:22.551
That's our case.

14:22.590 --> 14:24.626
That's how illegal guns
get out on the street.

14:24.660 --> 14:26.480
So, do you want to buy it?

14:26.530 --> 14:28.521
Do we need it?

14:28.560 --> 14:29.492
I don't know.

14:29.530 --> 14:31.088
Do you?

14:34.540 --> 14:37.532
I was checking on a court date
and I found out.

14:39.110 --> 14:41.101
You passed on the lawsuit.

14:42.210 --> 14:44.644
So, what are we doing here?

14:49.280 --> 14:52.579
Ten years ago, a drug dealer
named Jeffrey Spellman

14:52.620 --> 14:56.511
was convicted of double
murder in the 24th Ward.

14:56.560 --> 14:58.425
At his sentencing hearing,
he threatened

14:58.460 --> 15:00.052
to kill his lavwer
when he got out.

15:00.100 --> 15:02.159
You were his lavwer?

15:03.570 --> 15:06.994
I also spoke last week
at his parole hearing.

15:07.040 --> 15:09.031
He saw you speak?

15:10.670 --> 15:13.377
He'd made
subsequent threats.

15:14.680 --> 15:16.102
Has he been released?

15:16.140 --> 15:18.244
They decide on Friday.

15:18.280 --> 15:19.941
Okay.

15:19.980 --> 15:21.345
You need a gun.

15:21.380 --> 15:23.348
No, the thing is, I've
been in the forefront

15:23.390 --> 15:24.584
of gun control
my entire life.

15:24.620 --> 15:26.713
My father wrote
the first legislation

15:26.750 --> 15:28.479
into the Illinois constitution.

15:28.520 --> 15:29.714
You need something
easy to shoot.

15:29.760 --> 15:32.524
Light on recoil,
9mm-- a Beretta.

15:32.560 --> 15:34.619
No, this was a mistake.

15:36.230 --> 15:37.424
Look, I know you're my boss,

15:37.470 --> 15:39.461
and I'll do
whatever you want.

15:41.240 --> 15:43.538
You spoke at a killer's
parole hearing

15:43.570 --> 15:45.606
and he saw you speak
against his release.

15:45.640 --> 15:48.700
That's what I'd call
a volatile situation.

15:48.740 --> 15:50.139
So listen to me on this.

15:50.180 --> 15:51.670
You need a gun.

15:55.320 --> 15:58.619
It was a task force focusing
on fraudulent real estate deals.

15:58.650 --> 16:01.483
And these deals
were called "land flips"?

16:01.520 --> 16:03.454
Yes.
And as you understood it,

16:03.490 --> 16:05.549
there was an attempt
to buy land, cheaply,

16:05.590 --> 16:06.784
through fraudulent means,

16:06.830 --> 16:09.594
near the stadiums that were
to be built for the Olympics?

16:09.630 --> 16:10.767
Yes, sir.

16:10.800 --> 16:12.529
And during
the time you were

16:12.570 --> 16:14.458
heading up this
task force,

16:14.500 --> 16:16.092
you were approached
by Mr. Childs

16:16.140 --> 16:18.700
to keep an eye on Mr. Florrick,
isn't that correct?

16:21.640 --> 16:23.676
