for this task force.

16:28.750 --> 16:29.910
Objection, Your Honor.

16:29.950 --> 16:34.011
I have no idea why you are
objecting to that, Mr. Landry.

16:34.060 --> 16:35.516
A leading question,
Your Honor.

16:35.560 --> 16:39.348
I know I might need a scorecard
here, Mr. Landry.

16:39.390 --> 16:41.620
Isn't Mr. Brody
a hostile witness?

16:41.660 --> 16:43.161
Isn't he on your side?

16:43.200 --> 16:44.622
It's still leading,
Your Honor.

16:44.670 --> 16:47.537
Overruled. _
You may answer the question.

16:47.570 --> 16:49.162
Yes.

16:49.200 --> 16:52.101
