to object,

18:30.840 --> 18:32.728
and, yes, I need to sustain.

18:32.770 --> 18:35.238
I'm sorry, Your Honor.
We won't let that happen again.

18:35.280 --> 18:36.872
Now, I have to ask you

18:36.910 --> 18:39.799
