19:21.490 --> 19:23.958
So I suppose I--
I don't know--

19:23.990 --> 19:25.480
I did it just
to get back at her.

19:25.530 --> 19:27.896
And Colin was too
happy to help.

19:27.930 --> 19:29.898
He used to make
me do things.

19:29.930 --> 19:31.659
You know, things his wife
wouldn't do.

19:31.700 --> 19:34.533
Like the time he
had me tie up his...
(stammering)

19:34.570 --> 19:36.868
I think that
that is enough.

19:36.900 --> 19:38.663
I'm just going to sit down.

19:40.340 --> 19:41.170
Thank you.

19:41.210 --> 19:43.872
Great job, Daniel,
just outstanding.

19:43.910 --> 19:45.502
Did you see Childs?

19:45.550 --> 19:47.211
