21:20.910 --> 21:23.674
Jackie has been
helping out on weekdays

21:23.710 --> 21:25.075
while I'm at work,

21:25.110 --> 21:26.702
and I think
she should continue--

21:26.750 --> 21:28.809
picking the kids up
from school, making dinner...

21:30.050 --> 21:31.711
And we don't have a study.

21:31.750 --> 21:34.787
I still have your old
rolltop desk; it's in storage.

21:34.820 --> 21:37.459
I will move it
to the dining room.

21:37.490 --> 21:39.458
Okay?

21:39.490 --> 21:41.094
Do you love me?

21:41.130 --> 21:43.360
I do.

21:43.400 --> 21:45.925
