extraordinary.

24:54.960 --> 24:57.281
She said that you tried
to strangle her.

24:57.320 --> 24:59.288
That's a bit melodramatic.

24:59.330 --> 25:00.820
Yes, I know
it is, but

25:00.860 --> 25:02.953
my mom always used to say
"When you don't know,

25:03.000 --> 25:04.160
ask," so...

25:04.200 --> 25:05.269
