25:05.300 --> 25:06.324
Certainly.

25:06.370 --> 25:09.828
Carolyn and I were
practitioners of breath play.

25:09.870 --> 25:11.303
I'm sorry,
what is

25:11.340 --> 25:12.932
breath play?
Well, I'm sure

25:12.970 --> 25:15.734
they have it in Michigan,
too, Miss Crozier.

25:15.780 --> 25:18.305
Breath play is
erotic asphyxiation.

25:18.350 --> 25:20.204
Carolyn liked
the feeling

25:20.250 --> 25:23.549
of being strangled when
she was having sex.

25:27.250 --> 25:30.583
Oh, I think
I'd better sit down now.

25:32.590 --> 25:34.649
Your witness.

25:36.660 --> 25:38.662
WILL:
Okay, we go on the offensive.

25:38.700 --> 25:40.258
I'm not going to let
some 26-year-old

25:40.300 --> 25:41.995
law school grad get
the better of me.

25:42.040 --> 25:42.995
It's an act.

25:43.040 --> 25:44.166
Well, it's working.

25:44.210 --> 25:45.802
If we can't prove
our guy is innocent,

25:45.840 --> 25:47.899
