25:47.940 --> 25:49.032
What about
the plaintiff?

25:49.080 --> 25:51.207
_ Charlotte?
The jury felt sorry for her.

25:51.250 --> 25:52.342
She lost her mother.

25:52.380 --> 25:53.472
