40:41.600 --> 40:43.659
SWEENEY:
Mrs. Florrick.

40:44.870 --> 40:46.508
I brought you something.

40:46.540 --> 40:49.008
A token of my esteem.

40:56.950 --> 40:58.508
I thought it, somehow,

40:58.550 --> 41:00.586
strangely appropriate for you.

41:03.020 --> 41:04.214
You did it, didn't you?

41:04.260 --> 41:05.818
Did what?

41:05.860 --> 41:07.088
Killed her.

41:07.130 --> 41:08.085
Your wife.

41:08.130 --> 41:09.825
And then you

41:09.860 --> 41:11.225
buried her
in Charlotte's yard.

41:11.260 --> 41:13.592
IfI did that,

41:13.630 --> 41:16.531
why would I leave
the skull in my yard?

41:16.570 --> 41:17.992
To point us to Charlotte.

41:18.040 --> 41:20.508
You're being paranoid,
Mrs. Florrick.

41:20.540 --> 41:23.008
Sometimes things are
as they seem.

41:23.040 --> 41:26.077
The unlikely maneuver
is exactly that--

41:26.110 --> 41:27.771
unlikely.

41:30.050 --> 41:31.244
I have to go.

41:31.280 --> 41:32.679
Congratulations.

41:35.820 --> 41:38.983
You just have
to trust people.

41:41.030 --> 41:43.021
Enjoy the picture.

